                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Four Months.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">THOMAS TRUELOVE</hi>, <hi rend="italic">the Younger</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
